snippet.title: Final Beta Official Trailer | VEILED EXPERTS
snippet.description:
A new battle awaits your participation — VEILED EXPERTS returns to Steam for the Final Beta Test on March 30th.
Sign-up Now: https://nexon.link/5eM

Free-to-Play 5v5 tactical shooter where agents with unique Lepton skills meet action-packed gun mechanics.


—

MUSIC
Artist Name: ReauBeau
Track Title: Pressure (Feat. RIEИK)

🎵 Pressure Lyrics: 
Just breath in
hearts beating
any moment now
It’s that final hour
release your
inner demons
we’re on a mission now x3
we better make it count
 
pumped up with adrenaline 
arms up for the winning team
agents are you ready now
cuz we’re not holding back down
Get on top 
Cause we own 
a spot on_ the throne ,
we call the shots
Not gon’ stop
well make you run
 
Just breath in
hearts beating
any moment now
It’s that final hour x2
 
Are you feeling the PRESSURE? 
we are here for the crown
your enemies 
it’s hit n run 
we take you down
Make way for the legends
for the victory now 
dont make a sound
I got your back 
now take’em out.
Are you feeling the PRESSURE? 
Are you feeling the PRESSURE? 
Are you feeling the PRESSURE?


ReauBeau’s sonic journey started at the very roots of his present future bass undertakings. Due to astrong love for hiphop during his formative years, his passion spurred into the restless fiddling andfine-tuning art of conveying finer (and often ineffable) emotions through the craft of composition.His sound has emerged into a versatile blend of (future)bass and trap with a touch of euphoria.

📌 Pressure Official Release link: https://orcd.co/dyvjmv6
📌 ReauBeau's Website: https://www.reaubeau.com
📌 ReauBeau's Linktree: https://linktr.ee/reaubeau
